      "name": "Healthcare Working Group May General Meeting",
      "date": "2026-05-21T18:30:00Z",
      "date_formatted": "6:30 PM, Thursday May 21, 2026",
      "month_year": "2026-05",
      "month_label": "May 2026",
      "status": "confirmed",
      "description": "<p>Join our healthcare working group and the ascendant movement behind Zohran's inspiring Mayoral upset. We are an organizing space for health workers, patients, DSA-curious members of the public, and healthcare-curious DSA members building the movement to de-commodify healthcare. Plug in, meet new people, join upcoming actions, and help build this plane while we are flying it.</p><p>This is an in-person meeting but if you can't make it there is a Zoom option, we will do our best to include you.</p>",
      "browser_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/healthcare-working-group-may-general-meeting-2",
      "signup_url": "https://actionnetwork.org/events/healthcare-working-group-may-general-meeting-2",
      "location": "320 W 37th St",
      "borough": "New York"
    }
  ],
